Glen Gordon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glen_Gordon 0 Glen Charles Gordon (March 13, 1914 – September 16, 1977) was an American actor. Among other roles, Gordon played the role of Fu Manchu in the 1956 television series The Adventures of Dr. Fu Manchu.
